Package com.vmware.nsx.trust_management

Class TrustManagementFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.nsx.trust_management.TrustManagementFactory
  • public class TrustManagementFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    TrustManagementFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.nsx.trust_management package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
